{"type":"message","id":"2010560f","parentId":"304a6873","timestamp":"2026-06-03T03:48:31.011Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Well, that's bad. The `git submodule update --remote --merge` tried to fetch and merge the latest from the remote tracking branch for each submodule, but DidaFramework has merge conflicts. This isn't the right approach.\n\nLooking at AGENTS.md more carefully:\n> - 遍历子模块，检查是否有 detached HEAD 状态\n> - 对 detached HEAD 的子模块，根据 `.gitmodules` 或 `git submodule status` 显示的分支名执行 `git checkout <branch>` 再 `git pull`\n> - 确保所有子模块都指向正确分支的最新提交\n\nSo the correct approach is: for each submodule, check if it's detached HEAD, and if so, checkout the correct branch and git pull. If it's already on a branch, just git pull.\n\nThe submodules are all on branches already (no `+` prefix for detached, though actually `+` means the hash doesn't match the index... let me re-read).\n\nActually in `git submodule status`:\n- No prefix = submodule checked out at correct commit (matching index)\n- `+` prefix = submodule checked out at a different commit than what the index expects\n- `-` prefix = submodule not initialized\n- `U` prefix = submodule has merge conflicts\n\nSo with `+` prefix on 4 of them, they're at the wrong commit. But they do have branch names (e.g., `heads/YYZY_1V1_V1.0_WeekVersion_0528`).\n\nSince DidaFramework had conflicts when I tried the merge approach, let me just do a simpler approach: for each submodule, cd in and `git pull`. But first, let me fix the DidaFramework state.\n\nActually, the better approach according to TOOLS.md is: for each submodule, check detached HEAD, and if not detached, just git pull.\n\nLet me clean up the DidaFramework mess first, then do individual git pull for each submodule.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"DidaFramework 有冲突了，我来处理每个子模块单独更新。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_eBeCxsQhQEtH9sxKYhmG4679","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\Assets\\DidaFramework; git merge --abort 2>$null; git checkout -- . 2>$null; Write-Output \"DidaFramework reset done\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":822,"output":544,"cacheRead":30080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31446,"cost":{"input":0.00011508,"output":0.00015232,"cacheRead":0.00084224,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0011096399999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780458506580,"responseId":"8147e0b7-24f0-4ded-a824-f80ddf631225"}}
