{"type":"message","id":"40d2af91","parentId":"bd54b053","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:04:29.584Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人说\"更新测试包\"。让我想想这是什么意思。\n\n\"更新测试服\"是我熟悉的客户端热更流水线流程。但主人说的是\"更新测试包\"，不是\"更新测试服\"。\n\n\"测试包\"（test package/build）可能是指：\n1. 构建一个 APK/IPA 安装包（而非热更资源）\n2. 打包并上传到某个分发平台\n\n让我搜索一下记忆看看有没有关于\"测试包\"或\"打包\"的记录。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_yuNhIlb8c4uMrO2QvWCi9421","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"更新测试包 打包 build apk 构建安装包"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":12919,"output":154,"cacheRead":22400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35473,"cost":{"input":0.0018086600000000001,"output":0.00004312,"cacheRead":0.0006272,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00247898}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780470265628,"responseId":"91cef1e1-0451-49d8-bbf8-221250be124b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ec26e9af","parentId":"40d2af91","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:04:30.824Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_yuNhIlb8c4uMrO2QvWCi9421","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"058fdd53e3cba9ec908de536ced7c1e6e9644e52d5e5ff745fb02fd03016106f\",\n      \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 38,\n      \"endLine\": 65,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.617662085506446,\n      \"snippet\": \"- ⏳ **待完成：** 扫码登录后走通提单流程\\n\\n### 登录方式选择\\n主人选了**微信扫码登录**，二维码页面已调通，扫一扫即可登录。\\n登录后保存 Cookie，后续分析提单页面结构（bug/需求表单字段）。\\n\\n## 同事白名单\\n\\n- **主人 Yousan(叶枝君)** `ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f` — 无限制\\n- **允许同事执行的任务：** 更新测试服、提单（TAPD 自动创建缺陷）\\n- **私聊限制（2026-05-20）：** 其他同事私聊时不提供任何服务，提示去开发群 @ 我使用功能\\n- **周以天（兵王）** `ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966` 已开放私聊权限，可直接私聊使用白名单内所有功能\\n\\n## 群组信息\\n\\n- **月圆之夜CCG开发群** → `oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77`\\n  - 兵王(周以天) open_id：`ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966`\\n  - 小骑士(谭佳钦) open_id：`ou_fc5144301797fb813a1fee33e1130ac3`\\n\\n## 飞书消息 @ 人规范\\n- 正确格式：`<at user_id=\\\"open_id\\\">显示名字</at>`\\n- ⚠️ `user_id` 属性值**必须用英文双引号包裹**，缺引号飞书不解析，变成普通文字\\n- 飞书按 user_id 解析显示名，`<at>` 内的名字只是兜底文本\\n\\n## TAPD 登录保活方案（2026-\\n\\nSource: MEMORY.md#L38-L65\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"MEMORY.md#L38-L65\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ab9828b1d5f4b4c41f337fd371e717dfae2d957bb9d8c15e2ac71fe59a3e1a85\",\n      \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 59,\n      \"endLine\": 81,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.5747271373120925,\n      \"snippet\": \"- ⚠️ `user_id` 属性值**必须用英文双引号包裹**，缺引号飞书不解析，变成普通文字\\n- 飞书按 user_id 解析显示名，`<at>` 内的名字只是兜底文本\\n\\n## TAPD 登录保活方案（2026-05-20 更新：双账号）\\n\\n### 两个账号\\n- **周以天**：提单用，cookie `tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json`\\n- **叶枝君**：备用，cookie `tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json`\\n- 主文件 `tapd_cookies.json` 保持为周以天（提单脚本默认读取）\\n\\n### 保活脚本\\n- **保活脚本：** `workspace/scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs`\\n- **用法：** `node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs`（默认周以天）/ `node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs yezhijun`\\n- **原理：** 每天 headless 访问一次 workspace 主页，TAPD 会自动续 `tapdsession` 7 天\\n- **状态文件：** `memory/tapd-keepalive-state-zhouyitian.json` / `memory/tapd-keepalive-state-yezhijun.json`\\n- **HEARTBEAT 集成：** `HEARTBEAT.md` 已配置，每天两个账号都要跑一次\\n- **退出码：** 0=成功续期 / 1=登录失效需扫码 / 2=脚本错误\\n- **失效\\n\\nSource: MEMORY.md#L59-L81\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"MEMORY.md#L59-L81\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"a3c82c1487a1398238cb56eb103b4bf98fabae64be5da26e9fddec683305ce86\",\n      \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 92,\n      \"endLine\": 115,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.5641688423801638,\n      \"snippet\": \"- **使用方式：** 每次触发技能前检查清单版本，比记忆中的新则重新从磁盘读取 SKILL.md\\n- 当前技能版本：gitlab-permission=v2, tapd-bug-create=v1, tapd-vsmode-story=v1\\n\\n## GitLab 登录保活（2026-05-21）\\n\\n- **保活脚本：** `workspace/scripts/gitlab_keepalive.mjs`\\n- **原理：** 每天 headless 访问一次 GitLab 首页，服务器 session 会自动续期\\n- **同时刷新 CSRF Token**（从首页 `<meta name=\\\"csrf-token\\\">` 提取）\\n- **状态文件：** `memory/gitlab-keepalive-state.json`\\n- **Cookie 文件：** `workspace/gitlab_cookies.json`\\n- **CSRF 文件：** `workspace/gitlab_csrf.json`\\n- **HEARTBEAT 集成：** `HEARTBEAT.md` 已配置，每天自动保活\\n- **退出码：** 0=成功续期 / 1=登录失效需 SSO 重登 / 2=脚本错误\\n- **失效救援：** 用 `headless: false` 跑 Playwright，访问 GitLab → 点 SSO → Keycloak 输 LDAP 密码\\n\\n## GitLab 权限管理 Skill（2026-05-22 更新）\\n\\n- **仅主人可用**，不开放给其他同事\\n- Skill 路\\n\\nSource: MEMORY.md#L92-L115\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"MEMORY.md#L92-L115\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ecd766e7fbd4fcc5f45a4caf46d9ef5b3ae8a6cc2509eb519817c1f53d3172f2\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-05-19.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 50,\n      \"endLine\": 75,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.6089142216988435,\n      \"snippet\": \"- 内容：DevOps 流水线触发更新测试服的完整流程\\n  - 支持任意 `dest` 参数（1v1_qa / 1v1_cehua2 / 1v1_test 等）\\n  - 支持自定义分支覆盖\\n- 更新同事白名单 `COLLEAGUE_WHITELIST.md`，细化任务分类\\n  - 同事可通过 `构建<服务器名>服` 指定不同目标\\n- 更新 MEMORY.md 记录 DevOps 保活配置\\n\\n## 网关自助重启脚本\\n- 创建 `scripts/restart_gateway.ps1`，支持延迟重启不把自己杀掉\\n- 主人说「重启」时直接用这个脚本\\n- 已在 TOOLS.md 和 MEMORY.md 记录\\n- 当前 session 是重启后的干净环境\\n\\n## 新建技能「memory-keeper」\\n- SKILL.md 定义了每次对话结束时自动保存技能和记忆的逻辑\\n- 分类归档到对应文件：TOOLS.md / MEMORY.md / 每日日志 / SKILL.md / 白名单\\n- 只有在有新信息时才记录，不冗余\\n\\n## 发现群聊里中招\\n- 主人在「月圆之夜CCG开发群」4 次说「@荷井花 更新qa服」，我都误设为热更（Unity）\\n- 原因：群聊 session 允许旧版 SKILL.md 包含「更新qa服」作为热更别名\\n- 今天的修复：拆分为两个独立技能，重启后项目生效\\n\\n## 技能重构（1v1服务器 → 通用服务器）\\n- **原技能:** `update-test-server`（更新1v1服务器）\\n- **新技能:** `update-server`（更新服务器）\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-05-19.md#L50-L75\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-05-19.md#L50-L75\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"40345f4bfd73663130eedad8860720103080e233f384b69b4cddde81029d768d\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-05-19.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 30,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.5856881615358793,\n      \"snippet\": \"# 2026-05-19 日志\\n\\n## 热更流水线修复\\n- 飞书群消息脚本 `feishu_send_group.mjs` 中 @ 人格式总是被引号转义搞坏\\n- **修复方案：** 删掉命令行传 `at` 字符串的方式，改为脚本内置模板 `hotupdate-ok` / `hotupdate-fail`，sub-agent 只传模板名\\n- 更新：TOOLS.md 中更新测试服的群通知命令改为模板名方式\\n\\n## DevOps 流水线探索\\n- 分析了 `devops.devcloud.ztgame.com` 的 DevOps 平台\\n- 成功用 Playwright + Cookie 登录（headed 模式）\\n- **保存 DevOps Cookie** 到 `workspace/devops_cookies.json`\\n- **创建 DevOps Cookie 保活脚本** `scripts/devops_keepalive.mjs`\\n  - 每天 headless 访问一次流水线页面续期\\n  - 状态文件 `memory/devops-keepalive-state.json`\\n  - 已加入 HEARTBEAT 自动运行\\n- 更新了 HEARTBEAT.md 中保活部分的文档\\n\\n### 1v1 流水线分析\\n\\n| 流水线 | 状态 | 最近构建 | 执行人 |\\n|-------|:----:|:--------:|-------|\\n| 1v1-测试服 | ✅ | #1083 | 敖亚军 |\\n| 1v1-测试服-热更新 | ✅ | #13（1年前） | menglimin |\\n|\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-05-19.md#L1-L30\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-05-19.md#L1-L30\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"77b840043ebc1d775ae3049230986690a19ef3b64cc3db0c45af6eeb01ad1e97\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-05-27.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 30,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.6106439149821296,\n      \"snippet\": \"# 2026-05-27 日志\\n\\n## 热更流水线修复\\n\\n### 问题\\n流水线内 GitPull 步骤即使取消勾选，在 batch mode 下仍被执行。\\n原因是 `RunHotUpdatePipeline()` 硬编码了 `selectedOnly: false`，导致所有有效步骤全部执行。\\n\\n### 修复\\n改了 `E:\\\\Solo\\\\nightoffullmoon\\\\client\\\\cardv\\\\Assets\\\\Editor\\\\BuildPipeline\\\\BuildPipeline.cs`：\\n- `RunHotUpdatePipeline()` 内 `selectedOnly: false` → `selectedOnly: true`\\n- 注释和日志也同步更新\\n\\n现在命令行跑流水线只执行勾选的步骤。\\n\\n### 流程变更\\n- 以前：主仓库 git pull，子模块由流水线内部 Git 拉新处理\\n- 现在：主仓库 + 所有子模块全部手动 git pull/checkout 更新，流水线不再负责拉新\\n- 需要检查子模块 detached HEAD 状态，切到正确分支再 pull\\n\\n### 执行结果\\n共跑了 4 次流水线：\\n1. ❌ 子模块 detached HEAD -> git更新失败\\n2. ❌ 修好子模块但 GitPull 仍执行 -> git更新失败\\n3. ❌ 取消勾选 GitPull 但 batch mode 无视勾选 -> git更新失败\\n4. ✅ selectedOnly=true 修复后成功\\n\\n## 更新测试包通知\\n补丁已推送到 CDN，版本 1.0.41（Android），开\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-05-27.md#L1-L30\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-05-27.md#L1-L30\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"debug\": {\n    \"backend\": \"builtin\",\n    \"effectiveMode\": \"n/a\",\n    \"searchMs\": 1022,\n    \"hits\": 6\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8678,"originalDetailKeys":["results","provider","model","fallback","citations","mode","debug"]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780470270823}}
{"type":"message","id":"7317cf6d","parentId":"ec26e9af","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:04:37.653Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see from `memory/2026-05-27.md` that at the end it says \"更新测试包通知\" - \"补丁已推送到 CDN，版本 1.0.41（Android）\". So \"更新测试包\" seems to be related to the hot update pipeline (推送热更包到 CDN).\n\nBut wait - that's exactly what \"更新测试服\" just did (the hot update pipeline run). The hot update pipeline:\n1. Builds asset bundles\n2. Uploads to CDN\n\nSo \"更新测试包\" and \"更新测试服\" might be the same thing - or \"更新测试包\" might specifically mean just hot update (asset bundle/CDN push), while \"更新测试服\" could be broader.\n\nActually, looking at the TOOLS.md:\n- **触发指令:** \"更新测试服\"\n- **本质:** Unity 热更流水线，更新客户端资源/代码\n\nAnd \"更新测试包\" might refer to:\n- Building a full APK/IPA install package (not just hot update)\n- Or it could be the same as hot update\n\nLet me look at what was logged on 2026-05-27:\n\n```\n## 更新测试包通知\n补丁已推送到 CDN，版本 1.0.41（Android）\n```\n\nSo \"更新测试包\" was mentioned in context of pushing patches to CDN via hot update. But the phrasing \"更新测试包通知\" might be from a notification message saying \"更新测试包\" (updating test build/package).\n\nActually, I think the user is asking me to do the same hot update pipeline. \"更新测试包\" and \"更新测试服\" seem to be used somewhat interchangeably from what I can see. Let me just ask the owner to clarify if this is the same \"热更\" pipeline I just ran, or if they mean something different like building a full APK.\n\nActually wait - I just did the hot update. The owner is saying \"更新测试包\" after I completed the hot update. This might mean they want me to do something different than what I just did. Let me think...\n\n\"测试包\" = test build package (APK/IPA)\n\"测试服\" = test server (hot update to test server CDN)\n\nThese are different things. \"更新测试包\" would mean building a new APK/IPA installer package. The hot update I just ran pushed asset bundles to CDN, but the actual game client apk/ipa hasn't been rebuilt.\n\nLet me ask for clarification since I don't have a specific pipeline defined for building APK packages.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，刚跑完的是热更（推资源到 CDN），你说的\"更新测试包\"是指打一个完整的 APK/IPA 安装包？还是和刚才的热更是一回事？\n\n如果是要打安装包的话，我目前没有对应的流水线信息——是走 Unity BuildPipeline 的打包步骤，还是 DevOps 流水线？能给我指个路吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3235,"output":625,"cacheRead":35456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39316,"cost":{"input":0.0004529,"output":0.00017500000000000003,"cacheRead":0.000992768,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001620668}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780470270825,"responseId":"016afb6b-c680-449c-97ff-5226e07036b2"}}
