{"type":"message","id":"e7cf5236","parentId":"5de9e367","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:21:54.112Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The hot update failed with Unity exit code 32 and multiple C# compilation errors. According to the rules:\n- ❌ 失败 → 只私聊通知主人，不在群里发失败消息\n\nI'm already in a private chat with the owner (this is a feishu channel), so I can just tell them directly. Let me summarize the errors.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"❌ **热更失败了**\n\nUnity 退出码 32，有编译报错：\n\n**C# 编译错误：**\n1. `GiftRecommendManager.cs` — `GiftRecommendUrlUtils` 找不到（2处）\n2. `BookControl.cs` — `BackPackBookControl` 找不到\n3. `XLuaGenAutoRegister.cs` — `AndroidPhoneCalendarSubWarpWrap` 不存在\n4. `SubActivityDataFactory.cs` — `SoloSubActivityData_CreatorActivity` 找不到\n5. 缺失生成文件：`TbLevel.cs`、`LevelConfig.cs`（Server/CardBase/ExcelConfig）\n\n看起来是代码层面的引用缺失，可能是刚拉的新代码依赖了还没生成的配置/注册文件。你看看需要我先处理哪些？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1051,"output":244,"cacheRead":54912,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56207,"cost":{"input":0.00014714,"output":0.00006832000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001537536,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001752996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780471310463,"responseId":"99d4a52c-8acd-4422-b803-c088576946e6"}}
