{"type":"message","id":"58588451","parentId":"ff631c12","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:45:28.331Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人说\"更新测试服\"，这就是客户端热更流水线。但是刚才的编译错误还在，再跑一次大概率还是会失败。不过主人没提修代码的事，直接让更新测试服，可能他已经在本地处理了，或者这些错误他清楚。\n\n按流程走吧：\n1. 检查 Unity 进程\n2. 关 Unity Editor\n3. git pull 主仓库 + 子模块\n4. 跑热更流水线\n5. 检查结果\n\n不过 `selectedOnly: true` 那个修复我刚才已经改到文件里了（没提交），所以这次跑应该能跳过 GitPull 步骤。编译错误是代码问题，跟流水线配置无关，如果代码没修复，还是会报同样的错。\n\n但主人既然说了就让跑呗，可能他改了代码。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好嘞，跑热更！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_RJDPL07FH0QYyglKNsqN8935","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Process -Name \"Unity\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Stop-Process -Force; Write-Output \"Done\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":17641,"output":244,"cacheRead":39040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56925,"cost":{"input":0.00246974,"output":0.00006832000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00109312,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0036311800000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780472724026,"responseId":"241a5404-a339-4eaf-b639-c406dd2db884"}}
