{"type":"message","id":"eabd3e4f","parentId":"ce2083bb","timestamp":"2026-06-03T12:30:32.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Even with `--all`, the May 27 morning commits are missing. This means those commits were in a different branch entirely. Let me check the full history without time filter to find them.\n\nActually, I remember that in my very first query (without --author filter), I saw those commits from May 27 morning with format `%H|%ai|%an|%s`:\n\n```\n2026-05-27 14:51:00 +0800|yezhijun|--bug=1016759 --user=叶枝君 【1v1】装备皮肤后显示白块错误 https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/s/1495740\n2026-05-27 11:32:34 +0800|yezhijun|--story=1038703 --user=叶枝君 【0528】周版本 英雄皮肤语音替换 - 客户端 https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/s/1495554\n2026-05-27 11:30:03 +0800|yezhijun|--bug=1016765 --user=叶枝君 【1v1】普通英雄进入到的战斗后头像消失 https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/s/1495547\n2026-05-27 11:23:14 +0800|yezhijun|--bug=1016758 --user=叶枝君 【1v1】没有皮肤的英雄背景显示错误 https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/s/1495477\n```\n\nAnd also:\n```\n2026-05-27 18:26:38 +0800|yezhijun|资源清理\n2026-05-27 17:39:44 +0800|yezhijun|Timeline镜像工具\n2026-05-27 16:19:31 +0800|yezhijun|Timeline镜像测试\n2026-05-27 15:52:16 +0800|yezhijun|传说皮肤使用不同的背景\n```\n\nWait, let me look at the first query again:\n\n```\n621f883f52bd6ae7d33291d44d62fb718a5c21e1|2026-06-03 15:40:19 +0800|v-aoyajun|...\n...\nd39527207cab5a61addb23abe06e520ae52909d3|2026-06-02 10:52:09 +0800|yezhijun|代码优化\n9e66db00a4f371ac501eb81bc5c6b48ae5780666|2026-06-01 23:45:02 +0800|yezhijun|--bug=1016876 ...\n8f577624980c471b04eb9c47546a298237dc11bd|2026-06-01 21:40:16 +0800|v-aoyajun|...\n...\n6123c4af7abc1aec46d85e52f51419a105e5b989|2026-06-01 17:20:20 +0800|yezhijun|--bug=1016873 ...\n...\nd36b5c2c3b5af9fa61a7ae80f0c1759d37c3e65e|2026-05-29 16:31:38 +0800|tanjiaqin|...\n...\ndd7c390a25140a410732bfa82c5a43a065ad9c3e|2026-05-29 14:47:45 +0800|v-aoyajun|...\n...\n7c13f38677ba77ace7482303c6721a85443065b7|2026-05-29 11:34:13 +0800|wukaibin|...\n```\n\nSo that log only went back